sxt - simple x tube
===================
 ┌───────────────┐
 │████████████   │
 └───────────────┘
 ┌───┐ ┌─────────┐
 │67%│ │         │
 │███│ │   045   │
 │███│ │         │
 └───┘ └─────────┘

sxt draws tubes and
sometimes text.

features
--------
* fifo interaction
* optional text support
* xresources config
* featherweight

anti-features
-------------
* absolutely no dbus support, try tiramisu
* background service / daemon
* mouse / keyboard input
* wayland support

